meta.name: The Little Tibet
meta.about: The Little Tibet is a platform for indigenous Himalayan craftsman to showcase their work of passion for long term sustainable livelihoods and wellbeing. Places such as Tibet, Nepal, India, Kashmir, have been our universe and our admiration.
